  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    WrsBindingItem
    public class BindingItemAttribute
extends BindingItemWithMetaData
    This class is container of one attribute of binding item. It serves as a marker In WRS-request the Attribute element presents as <Columns> ... <C bRef="column1"> <A name="caption" bRef="column2"/> </C> ... </Columns> See WRS-request XSD for more information about Columns and Attributes rules.
